    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated. Seven factors were formally assessed with required and achieved levels documented; all seven meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. The remaining six factors were addressed through documented assessment activities. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support use of the CFD model to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The model is accepted for the stated COU.",
